Title: Maybelline Combo(Set of 3)
Description: Maybelline Volum Express Colossal Waterproof Mascara 10 ml(Glam Black)-Maximum volume and maximum definition for your eyes – that’s what you get from a single swipe of Maybelline’s Volum Express Mascara in the shade Glam Black.WaterproofThe superior formula is waterproof and holds its own when you swim, run for cover in the rain or shed a few tears.Smudge ResistantThe jet black color clings to your lashes and stays put even if you accidentally touch your eyes. Imagine a formula that is waterproof and smudge proof – now that’s something!Collagen Enriched FormulaThe unique formula is enriched with collagens that plump lashes one by one and provide you thick lashes that almost reach the sky!No ClumpsThe creamy formula goes smoothly and separates each lash without making them clump together for a gorgeous finish.Contact Lens SafeTested and found safe by ophthalmologists, this waterproof mascara is safe to use by contact lens wearers and doesn’t cause irritation.Define your eyes with those dramatic and thick lashes and stay gorgeous, come rain or shine.Maybelline Clean Express Total Clean Express Eye & Lip Makeup Remover(70 ml)-With Fast Acting Dissolving Agents, With Non Greasy Residue, Moisturizes Eye Area, Removes Stubborn, Waterproof and Long Lasting Eye Makeup, Dermatologist and Allergy Tested, Cleanses Lids and Lashes Immediately.Maybelline Hypersharp Liner 0.5 g(Black)-Maybelline gives you this super sharp and ultra-thin Eyestudio Hypersharp Liner in the shade black that helps you draw that precise and sharp line.0.05 mm Fine Tip Liquid LinerWith a tip so thin and sharp, this Maybelline Liquid Liner making drawing that Cleopatra tilt so much easier.Most Precise LineDraw precision line strokes with ease and get noticed and appreciated wherevr you go.WaterproofWhat’s more, even if you shed a tear or walk in the rain, you are assured of a liner that doesn’t run.Easy Removal by Warm WaterAll you have to do to remove this eyeliner is rub it off with a cotton pad dipped in warm water.Smudge-proofAnd of course, you get the smudge-proof and great staying power of this Hypersharp Liner.

Title: Faiza Herbal Beuty Cream Clears Pimples,Wrinkles,Marks(Set of 1)
Description: Beautify Your Skin this Year By indulging in the Faiza Beauty Cream. A Perfect Addition to Your Daily Skincare Routine Is this Cream Which Not Only Brightens Your Skin, But Makes It Smooth, Free Of Blemishes And Dark Spots.It Has technologically Proven Advanced Formulation With A Special Rapid Absorption Formula that Provides triple Action On Skin - Lightening, Whitening And Brightening With the Help Of Natural ingredients that Penetrate Deep into the Skin to Provide Complete Enduring Action. It Helps in Removing Dullness And Hyper Pigmentation Providing A Great Feel, An Even Better Look & Smooth Healthy touch For Your Skin. Faiza Beauty Cream Is Purely Herbal Cream.Benefits:* It Removes the Most Prominent Pimples, Cists, Gloom And Other Acne Problems.* It Removes Wrinkles, Marks, Hives Even Dark Circles Under the Eyes And turns the Skin into White. * Fast And Rapid Skin Whitening Action.* Provides Salon Like Sheer Matte Finish to Your Skin.* Even Skin tone, Clear And Smoother Skin.* Clinically Proven to Be Safe And Effective.* Helps Restore Purity, Radiance & Refined Facial Contours.* Its Anti-Oxidants Properties Keep Your Skin Look Healthy And Youthful.* Protects Your Skin From the Damage From Sun Rays And Pollution.Directions to UseBefore Going to Sleep, Wash Your Face With A Good Soap And Dry Gently, Apply A Small Amount Of Faiza Beauty Cream And Massage Gently into the Skin So that the Cream Could Penetrate inte the Skin. in the Morning Wash Your Face With Soap. For Seven Days Regular Use Of the Cream Would Make Conspicuous Changes Making Your Skin Acne Free, Fresh And Charming. Keep Using the Cream till You Achieve the Required Results. Even After that Keep Using the Cream At Least twice A Week, So that It Could Protect Your Skin From the Fatigues Like Dryness, Sunlight, Dust and Pollution

Description: Merit Black Seed Oil is an oil derived by pressing the seeds of the Nigella Sativa plant. The seeds are also commonly referred to as black cumin. Black Seed/ Kalonji Oil is derived from cold-pressing Nigella Sativa seeds. The cold-pressed method of deriving Black Seed Oil ensures that the properties of the Black Seed are retained.. In Islam, Kalonji or the black-seed is regarded as one of the greatest forms of healing medicine available. According to tradition, the Prophet Muhammad (Sallallahu Alaihi wa Sallam) described black seed as a cure for every disease except death. It has been traditionally used for a variety of conditions and treatments related to respiratory health, stomach and intestinal health, kidney and liver function, circulatory and immune system support, as analgesic, anti-inflammatory, anti-allergic, antioxidants, anticancer, antiviral and for general well-being. Black Seed oil is used for numerous health and beauty reasons throughout the world. Title: Eraser Anti-Acne and Pimple Cream(12 g)
Description: A supremely effective and natural treatment for acne and pimples specially formulated by our team of Ayurvedic doctors. Eraser Anti-Acne & Pimple Cream is a safe and effective Ayurvedic Formulation that naturally treats acne and pimples in a few days.The cream works in two ways. Firstly it kills skin bacteria that are a common cause of pimples. Secondly it soaks up excessive oil to control acne & pimples caused by oil-water imbalances in the skin.Comprising of ingredients like Neem & Haldi (Turmeric), that have been known through the ages for their anti-bacterial properties and Khariya Mitti & Ghandak, that help dry boils and soak excessive oil present in acne prone skin, it?s a complete acne treatment. Along with treating acne effectively, the Ayurvedic formulation gently heals your skin with its cooling and antiseptic properties.For best results and reinforced effectiveness, use this product alongside Eraser Anti-Acne and Pimple Face Wash or Eraser Anti-Acne & Pimple Soap.Answered below by our Team of Qualified Ayurvedic DoctorsQ) How do I use Eraser Anti-Acne & Pimple Cream?A) This product works best as an overnight cream. Prior to use wash your face thoroughly with a little soap and lukewarm water at bedtime. Or for better results you can use Eraser Anti-Acne & Pimple Soap or Facewash.Then apply a thick layer of Eraser Anti Acne & Pimple Cream directly on the pimple(s) and a fine layer on other affected areas where pimples often erupt.Allow it to dry. Wash it off with lukewarm water in the morning. During application you will experience a slight tingling sensation, which is a clear indication that the cream is working. A little redness may also occur which will subside, as the pimple dries and heals.Q) Can this product also be used by men?A) Yes ? all of our products have been formulated with both males and females in mind. In fact around 50% of our consumers are male. So if you are a male don?t feel hesitant at all, in trying out our effective Ayurvedic products.Q) How often should I apply Eraser Anti-Acne & Pimple Cream?A) We advise at least one application a day ? preferably at bedtime. However for best results you should apply the cream 2 to 3 times a day. When you purchase the cream, the packaging also contains more detailed instructions on how to apply the cream.Q) How long does it take for Eraser Anti Acne & Pimple Cream to work?A) You should begin to see results within a few days of applying the cream on the affected area ? as the pimple dries out.Q) Can I go out in the sun after using this cream?A) Yes - you can go out in the sun after applying Eraser Anti-Acne & Pimple Cream.Q) Who is affected by acne? And what are the causes of acne and pimples? What else can I do to control my acne and pimples?A) It?s a common myth that acne affects adolescents only. Acne and pimples can affect anyone ? regardless of their age or gender.The reasons for acne include stress, anxiety or hormone imbalance during adolescence.A common cause of acne and pimples is excess oil in your skin. The reason this happens is that your skin contains sebaceous glands ? which naturally produce a substance called sebum. Sebum helps keep your skin soft and moisturized. However in many cases your sebaceous glands can start producing excessive oil (sebum). Dead skin cells then begin to clump together ? forming a plug. This plug traps dead cells, bacteria and oil within it ? and swells up to form acne. The whole process of acne formation takes 2-3 weeks and it culminates in a pimple.In many instances it is quite difficult to cure acne - instead you can seek to control and manage the problem using our Eraser Anti-Acne & Pimple Cream ? alongside daily use of Eraser Anti-Acne & Pimple Soap or Eraser Anti-Acne & Pimple Facewash.`

Title: NATURAL POMEGRANATE PEEL POWDER(200 g)
Description: #1 It fights acne, pimples and rashesHow to use it: Take a handful of sun-dried pomegranate peels and roast them over a hot tava or a deep-bottomed pan. Allow them to cool and grind them in a grinder or mixer. Make a paste of this powder with lemon juice or rose water and apply it all over your face, especially on your pimples or acne. Let it dry for a while then wash it off thoroughly with lukewarm water.#2 It prevents wrinkles and other signs of ageingHow to use it: Take two spoonfuls of sun-dried and powdered peel and add little milk to it. If you have oily skin, add rose water to the powder instead of milk and make a paste out of it. Apply this paste on your face and keep it till it dries. Wash your face with lukewarm water and try using the powder at least twice a week for better results.#3 It acts as a natural moisturiserHow to use it: Grind sun-dried pomegranate peels in a mixer and empty the powder into a clean bowl. Make sufficient powder to last you for a week and store it in an airtight container. Take two spoonfuls of the powder and mix well with some yoghurt to make a paste out of it. Apply this paste on your face and neck and leave for 10 minutes. Next, wash it off with cold water.#4 It acts as an effective facial scrubHow to use it: Take two spoonfuls of sun-dried pomegranate powder and add one spoon of brown sugar to it. To make a paste, add one spoon of honey, one spoon of avocado oil or any essential oil of your choice and mix well. Next, scrub your face with the homemade scrub and massage thoroughly. Wash it off with water to get smooth supple skin. However, don’t forget to use a toner and a moisturiser after scrubbing.#5 It acts as natural sunscreenHow to use it: Make a powder with sun-dried pomegranate peels and store in an airtight container. Mix this powder with your lotion or cream, preferably 20 minutes before leaving the house. Alternatively, you can also mix the powder with some essential oils and apply on your face, if you wish to use a natural sunscreen.#6 It arrests hair loss and prevents dandruffHow to use it: Mix dried-pomegranate peel powder with your hair oil. Next, apply it on the roots of your hair and massage thoroughly. You can wash your hair with a mild shampoo after two hours of the application or keep it overnight as per your convenience.Pomegranate peels help to restore your overall healthHere is how the peels can help one combat various health crisis and boost overall health:#7 It’s an excellent home remedy for sore throat#8 It protects against heart disease#9 It improves dental hygiene#10 It helps improve gut-health
